<section id="TaskDesc">
<div class="page-header">
<h1>Task Description <small>What is this task all about?</small></h1>
</div>
<p>
	In this task, you will be annotating scientific papers with details about the <b>type</b> of citations. When you annotate for the scientific papers, you will need to read through a set of <b>citing papers</b> to look for <b>citing sentences</b> and a set of <b>cited papers</b> to look for the <b>cited information</b>. Finally for each citation, you will key in details into the <b>working file</b>.
</p>
<h2>Task Objective</h2>
<p>
The objective of this task is to gather manual annotations for our research. We wish to determine the type of the citation. There is a total of <b>3 types</b> of citation.
</p>
<h2>Task Requirements</h2>
<p>
	You will need to download the scientific papers, and the working file to complete the task. You will annotate for the scientific papers, entering the details into the working file. At the end of the task, you are only required to submit your annotation in the <b>working file</b>.
</p>
</section>

